snippet.title: I Love Softball (Famicom) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full game of I Love Softball, a 1989 softball video game by Marionette and Coconuts Japan.

I tacked a clip of a home run onto the end to share what that looks like.

For more info, check out the baseball video game encyclopedia here: https://30-30.club/wiki/i-love-softball/
